  "richText": {
    "data": {},
    "content": [
      {
        "data": {},
        "content": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": "With flexbox there is now a simple way to let your footer stick to the bottom, when there is not enough content, and make it static when there is.",
            "nodeType": "text"
          }
        ],
        "nodeType": "paragraph"
      },
      {
        "data": {},
        "content": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": "At first we need the HTML-skeleton. One wrapper, in this case the body-element itself, and at least 2 child-elements. I'm also including the header here, because it is often used in this kind of arrangement.",
            "nodeType": "text"
          }
        ],
        "nodeType": "paragraph"
      },
      {
        "data": {
          "target": {
            "metadata": {
              "tags": []
            },
            "sys": {
              "space": {
                "sys": {
                  "type": "Link",
                  "linkType": "Space",
                  "id": "lvgw6if4imbu"
                }
              },
              "id": "1Oc2gkswfh7vFMM2yQUCvA",
              "type": "Entry",
              "createdAt": "2021-05-26T10:59:57.856Z",
              "updatedAt": "2021-05-26T10:59:57.856Z",
              "environment": {
                "sys": {
                  "id": "master",
                  "type": "Link",
                  "linkType": "Environment"
                }
              },
              "revision": 1,
              "contentType": {
                "sys": {
                  "type": "Link",
                  "linkType": "ContentType",
                  "id": "codeBlock"
                }
              },
              "locale": "en-US"
            },
            "fields": {
              "internalName": "Flex footer html",
              "code": "<body>\n  <div class=\"Header\"></div>\n  <div class=\"Content\"></div>\n  <div class=\"Footer\"></div>\n</body>",
              "syntax": "html"
            }
          }
        },
        "content": [],
        "nodeType": "embedded-entry-block"
      },
      {
        "data": {},
        "content": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": "And now give the ",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ],
            "value": "body",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": " ",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ],
            "value": "display: flex",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": " and ",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ],
            "value": "flex-direction: column",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": " to stack the three child elements vertically.\nTo support IE 11 we also need those styles on the ",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ],
            "value": "html",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": " element.\nAlso the ",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ],
            "value": "body",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": " elements need to be at least ",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ],
            "value": "100vh",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": " in height.",
            "nodeType": "text"
          }
        ],
        "nodeType": "paragraph"
      },
      {
        "data": {
          "target": {
            "metadata": {
              "tags": []
            },
            "sys": {
              "space": {
                "sys": {
                  "type": "Link",
                  "linkType": "Space",
                  "id": "lvgw6if4imbu"
                }
              },
              "id": "rveQfgptirRw77rpH1HIn",
              "type": "Entry",
              "createdAt": "2021-05-26T11:01:05.559Z",
              "updatedAt": "2021-05-26T11:01:05.559Z",
              "environment": {
                "sys": {
                  "id": "master",
                  "type": "Link",
                  "linkType": "Environment"
                }
              },
              "revision": 1,
              "contentType": {
                "sys": {
                  "type": "Link",
                  "linkType": "ContentType",
                  "id": "codeBlock"
                }
              },
              "locale": "en-US"
            },
            "fields": {
              "internalName": "flex footer css",
              "code": "html,\nbody {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n}\nbody {\n  min-height: 100vh;\n}",
              "syntax": "css"
            }
          }
        },
        "content": [],
        "nodeType": "embedded-entry-block"
      },
      {
        "data": {},
        "content": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": "The trick now is to give the ",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ],
            "value": ".Content",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": "-element the ",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ],
            "value": "flex-grow: 1",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": " so the footer gets pushed to the bottom.\nYou also can add ",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ],
            "value": "flex-shrink: 0",
            "nodeType": "text"
          },
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": " to the other elements so that they don't get squished when the viewport is too small.",
            "nodeType": "text"
          }
        ],
        "nodeType": "paragraph"
      },
      {
        "data": {
          "target": {
            "metadata": {
              "tags": []
            },
            "sys": {
              "space": {
                "sys": {
                  "type": "Link",
                  "linkType": "Space",
                  "id": "lvgw6if4imbu"
                }
              },
              "id": "2l5WW5WP6RqtAo5AJRASUO",
              "type": "Entry",
              "createdAt": "2021-05-26T11:01:49.803Z",
              "updatedAt": "2021-05-26T11:01:49.803Z",
              "environment": {
                "sys": {
                  "id": "master",
                  "type": "Link",
                  "linkType": "Environment"
                }
              },
              "revision": 1,
              "contentType": {
                "sys": {
                  "type": "Link",
                  "linkType": "ContentType",
                  "id": "codeBlock"
                }
              },
              "locale": "en-US"
            },
            "fields": {
              "internalName": "footer flex css 2",
              "code": ".Header,\n.Footer {\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n.Content {\n  flex-grow: 1;\n}",
              "syntax": "css"
            }
          }
        },
        "content": [],
        "nodeType": "embedded-entry-block"
      },
      {
        "data": {},
        "content": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": "And voilá your footer is at the bottom all the time.",
            "nodeType": "text"
          }
        ],
        "nodeType": "paragraph"
      },
      {
        "data": {},
        "content": [
          {
            "data": {},
            "marks": [],
            "value": "The complete result:",
            "nodeType": "text"
          }
        ],
        "nodeType": "heading-2"
      },
